"   </a>",
"   <a class=\"icontxt textLink etacLink\" href=\"#\" title=\"Email graphic(s)\">",
"    Email",
"   </a>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Survival is poorer in patients with chest pain who have valvular regurgitation on echocardiography",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 327px; height: 448px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Kaplan Meier survival curves show that among 448 patients presenting to the emergency room with chest pain, the presence of more than mild mitral regurgitation (MR), tricuspid regurgitation (TR), or aortic regurgitation (not shown) is an independent predictor of mortality.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
